¬†

Manoj transitioned from a printing hardware development at a public company to storage development in fast pace startup environment, to ultra fast pace environment of Nutanix. Most recently, he was Director of Engineering in Enterprise Storage solutions division of SanDisk. Prior to that, he held several engineering roles at Pliant Technology, Electronics For Imaging, Synopsys and STMicroelectronics.

¬†

He brings with him over 15 years of experience building and scaling teams for delivering enterprise grade products.¬†Manoj received his Bachelors degree in Electrical Engineering from IIT Kanpur.                    









